  - On command from mobile app (via Firebase), capture image and upload to Firebase Storage, or start video streaming.
- **Implementation**: Refer to our [ESP32 + Firebase Integration Guide](#) for details.

### 2. Mobile App (Android/iOS)
- **Function**: User interface to view sensor data, control ESP32, receive AI alerts, and watch live video stream.
